attributes.title: Kingdom Hearts vs A Very Goofy Mystery
attributes.description: Burnie, Ashley, Gus, and Chad play Kingdom Hearts 3 while trying to unravel the story behind the games. They also discuss Frozen, digital licenses for games, Final Fantasy plots, what animal Goofy is, and more!

attributes.title: Crackdown 3 vs Michael's Origin Story
attributes.description: Burnie, Ashley, Gus, and Michael talk about Crackdown 3 with Microsoft Creative Director (and Bungie Veteran!) Joseph Staten. They also talk about how Michael got his job at Rooster Teeth, E3 predictions, the state of crossplay, collectibles and achievements in games, and more!

attributes.title: Anthem Vs Shooty Looty Gotta Get That Booty
attributes.description: Burnie, Ashley, Gus, and Chad play Anthem and discuss games as a service, loot shooters, the future of gaming, and more on this week's episode of Game Time!

attributes.title: Apex Legends vs The Keyboard Torture Method
attributes.description: Burnie, Gus, Chad, and Andrew bicker about who in the group is the true Kill Leader, the correct control scheme for Apex Legends, mouse and keyboard versus controller, and more on this week's episode of Game Time.

attributes.title: Resident Evil 2 vs Burnie's Zombie Problem
attributes.description: Burnie, Chad, Ashley, and Blaine try their hand at Resident Evil 2 and struggle against the traditional survival horror genre. They also talk about video game remakes and reboots, different types of zombies, games with limited save slots, good video game maps, different ping systems in video games, and more on this week's episode of Game Time.

attributes.title: The Sims 4 vs Ashley's Baby Bump
attributes.description: This week on Game Time Ashley, Burnie, Chad, Becca and Mush discuss becoming a parent, dealing with kids, dealing with your parents, painting slaves, bringing out your dark sim side and, being the "fun" parents. They also deal with Mush the demon cat.

attributes.title: Game Time LIVE from the Bumble Hive
attributes.description:
Thanks to Bumble for sponsoring this video!
 Ashley Jenkins and Barbara Dunkelman join Voice Actress Victoria Atkin for a special live episoe of Game Time from the Bumble Hive at SXSW! They talk about female video game protagonists, Horizon Zero Dawn and Skyrim, the small world of voice actors, attempting accents, and what got you into gaming.

attributes.title: Devil May Cry 5 Vs Gus' Pet Peeve
attributes.description: Ashley, Jon, Gus, Adam, and sleepy mush try to explain Devil May Cry 5's absurd story. They also talk about long game intros and load screens, starting new games, Sekiro excitement, Adam and Ashley's cats, Google Stadia, streaming games in 4k, what they've been playing, John Wick 3, using Phallic vs Yonic, and sleep studies .

attributes.title: Sekiro Vs the Ideal Male Form
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Ashley, Adam, and Chad as they discover what "Shadows Die Twice" means in Sekiro. They also discuss Aquaman's chiseled body, overly difficult games like Dark Souls, the most cheese game of all time, discovering you are colorblind, best april fools video game announcements, Activision and Bungie's breakup, the Halo MMO, the revival of fortnite, and the history of tetris.

attributes.title: Yoshi's Crafted World Vs Cold Dead Eyes
attributes.description: Join Chad, Ellie, Ashley, and Burnie as they explore the disgustingly cute game "Yoshi's Crafted World". They also talk about why people watch video games instead of playing them, hardcore platforming, Captain Marvel and the Marvel Cinematic Universe, Shazam, the "gamer lean", ping pong ball attacks, cloning dogs, their first video game, and the evolution of Sea of Thieves.

attributes.title: Xbox Game Clips Vs the Perfect Horse Dismount
attributes.description: On this week's Game Time, Burnie and Gavin watch through their library of game clips that they have created over their gaming career. They also discuss the best glitches, horse wrecks, Fallout 4's weird NPC's, persistent open worlds, and how much Xbox's game recording has changed.

attributes.title: Cuphead Vs Chad's Unraveling
attributes.description: Join Gus, Ellie, and Brian Gaar as they watch Chad go insane trying to play Cuphead on Switch. Join the group as they are plagued with the "compliment curse", talk old Nintendo games, their favorite platformer shooter, how accessible games should be, the hardest game they have ever beaten, standing up to SCHMUP, and discovering the difficulty that is Cuphead.

attributes.title: Mortal Kombat 11 VS Mortal Konflict Resolution
attributes.description: Join Ashley, Kyle, Chad, and Max as they discover that Mortal Kombat is just Kingdom Hearts for fighting bros. They also recap the ENTIRE Mortal Kombat storyline and talk about seamless video game cutscene transitions, fatalities that go too far, Ronda Rousey as Sonya Blade, Kotal Kahns Fursona, and gross insect stories.

attributes.title: Days Gone Vs the Rooster Teeth Zombie Plan
attributes.description: Burnie, Ashley, Chris, Blaine, and Mush discuss their zombie plan while playing Days Gone. They also talk about the future of zombie games, different types of zombies, shaving Matt at Extra Life, single player campaign games, starting a game after taking a break from it , the survive button and the punch button, cute zombie babies, correct zombie posture, the Christopher Lee scream, Burnie's perfect game, and the best fictional weapon you would want.

attributes.title: Sea of Thieves Vs Throwing Everyone Under The Boat
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Ashley, Chad, and Mush as they try to convince Gus that Sea of Thieves is a good game. They also talk about how Sea of Thieves has changed since it's launch, playing with multiple randoms online, Burnie's love for Ariana Grande, Chad's Sea of Thieves ADD, trying to do video game things in real life, and more!

attributes.title: Rage 2 Vs WoW Classic
attributes.description: Join Adam, Ashley, and Mush as they play through Rage 2 while Gus and Chad get sidetracked by WoW Classic announcements. They also discuss sassy brands on social media, dipping your fries in milkshakes, talking with ghosts, setting up raiding schedules, WildStar, sharing video game interests with your significant other and LAN parties on the road. Also Chad talks Warcraft, Warcraft, and more Warcraft.

attributes.title: Factorio Vs Gus' Robot Friends
attributes.description: Join Gus, Burnie, Chad, Ashley and Mush as they discover Factorio. Chad talks Conker's Bad Fur Day and assless jeans, Gus talks the intricacies of Factorio, Ashley talks banning gaming mods in the house and Giants: Citizen Kabuto,  Burnie discovers the Sea of Thieves Tutorial and starts a war on pitbulls. Mush escapes.

attributes.title: Skyrim VS a Bucket for Dorth-E
attributes.description: Join Gus, Barbara, Ashley, and Chad and Mush as they play Skyrim in 2019 with some minimal graphics mods. Ashley wonders what appliance Skyrim will end up on next, Chad reveals he has never played Portal 2, Barbara looks for her next Game of Throne-type addiction, Gus talks ordering pizza through linux scripts. Mush becomes a Dragon. Mod List: Static Mesh Improvement, Skyrim 2018 textures, Skyrim Flora Overhaul, Realistic Water Two, Better Roads.

attributes.title: Game Dev Tycoon Vs the E3 Shit Show
attributes.description: Join Chad, Ashley, Burnie, and Gus and Mush as they start their own game dev business while discussing E3 rumors and predictions. Gus creates the smash hit DungSim 2. Burnie complains about Animal Crossing. Ashley talks E3 rumors and leaks. Chad officially names Burnie as a Sea of Thieves Enthusiast. Mush climbs.

attributes.title: Void Bastards vs E3 Reactions
attributes.description: Join Gus, Adam, Chad, and Ryan as they go over E3 announcements while surviving space in Void Bastards. Gus talks about the best video game at E3. Adam is upset with Jedi: Fallen Order. Chad is hyped for Banjo-Kazooie in Smash Bros. Ryan wants to be put into cryostasis until 2020.

attributes.title: Cadence of Hyrule VS the #*$&ING LOST WOODS
attributes.description: Join Gus, Ashley, Chad, and Ellie and Mush as they find their rhythm with Cadence of Hyrule. Chad gets hooked with Zelda nostalgia. Ashley gets lost in the woods. Gus figures out bombs. Ellie talks about how dating Miles means she is always up to date on Nintendo. Mush gets the poop zooms.

attributes.title: State of Decay 2: Heartland VS Gus and the Police
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Gus, Ashley, Chad, and Mush as they survive the zombie apocalyse in State of Decay 2. Gus threatens the police. Chad tells tales of poopy parenting. Burnie talks about his addictions with mobile games. Ashley entertains the idea of a Persona Zombie game.

attributes.title: They are Billions Vs HORDE DAY
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Gus, Chris, Ashley, and Mush as they try the new "They are Billions" campaign mode. Chris becomes the Minister of Lightning. Gus heckles Burnie. Ashley talks about sex education. Burnie discovers a new hatred for trains. Mush judges Burnie.

attributes.description: Join Burnie, Gus, Ashley, Chad and Mush for a roller coaster Mario Party episode. Chad uses up his luck. Gus makes Burnie feel old. Burnie gets overwhelming power. Ashley gets a whole lot of nothing. Mush tries to play.

attributes.description: Join Ashley, Jeremy, Matt, Kyle, and Mush as they race to victory in Crash Team Racing. Jeremy explains Calus Bod. Matt dominates CTR. Ashley is hopeful for swole Witcher. Kyle explains the Crisis on Infinite Earth Superman. Mush makes friends with Jeremy.

attributes.description: Join Ashley, Miles, Blaine, Chad, and Mush as they shoot through Wolfenstein Youngblood. Ashley is confused by cat comfort. Miles talks about his hunting experiences. Blaine explains the Wolfenstein storyline. Chad plays on an itty bitty tiny WW2 screen. Mush Bite.

attributes.title: Portal 2 VS The Great YEET
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Ashley, Chad, Drew, and Mush as they start thinking with Portals. Burnie talks about his weird connection with Portal. Ashley yeets Chad. Drew experiences Portal 2. Mush camps out in his tent.

attributes.title: Diablo 3 Hardcore vs Fun Times Smoking Crack
attributes.description: Join Burnie, Ashley, and Sam as they watch Gus try and survive a hardcore Diablo 3 run. Gus struggles to survive. Burnie makes fun of Gus' mouse. Ashley looks into the top 5 adult diapers for hardcore gaming. Sam preps for WoW Classic.

attributes.description: Join Gus, Blaine, Chad, and Kyle as they get try and escape the Vicious Circle. Gus talks about early concepts for Vicious Circle. Blaine gets double teamed by a chicken. Chad gives some lesser known Vicious Circle tips. Kyle talks about Vicious Circle Lore.

attributes.description: Join Gus, Ellie, Chad, and Cole as they explore CONTROL. Ellie prioritizes defensive tactics. Gus embarrasses himself.  Chad is ready for WoW Classic. Cole learns about dude shadows.

attributes.description: Join Gus, Chad, Ellie, and Sam for some WoW Classic. Gus learns about VSCO Girls. Ellie pitches her RWBY MMO. Chad talks about his WoW staycation. Sam has strong opinions about your WoW control schemes.
